James T. Patterson - Grand Expectations: The United States, 1945-1974

From Audible dot com, Read by Robert Fass, 64 kbps

2010 Audible, published 1996, Winner of the 1997 Bancroft Prize. Volume 10 of the Oxford History of the United States.
